Date:		March 2017
KernelVersion:	4.15
Contact:	Christian Gromm <christian.gromm@microchip.com>
Description:
		This is to read back the configured data type of the channel.
		The following strings will be accepted:
			'control',
			'async',
			'sync',
			'isoc_avp'
